   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "The 2026 edition shows that commercial colocation and hyperscale facilities now provide more than two-thirds of Europe’s IT power, driven by the growing demand for cloud and AI."
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.germandatacenters.com/fileadmin/images/DCIRD-24/Data-Center-Impact-Report-Deutschland-2024_EN.pdf",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "1,955 MW IT power in Germany approx. ... 831 MW IT power in Frankfurt colocation data centers * Colocation and enterprise data centers > 50 kW"
  },
  {
